step_data.thought: I'm currently looking at a 404 Error page after attempting to access the sitemap directly via URL. I've already explored several main menu options including SYSTEM, STORES, CONTENT, and REPORTS without finding the Site Map link. The URL I tried (http://127.0.0.1:7780/admin/admin/dashboard/sitemap/) returned a 404 error, indicating this is not the correct path.\n\nIn Magento Admin, the Site Map could potentially be under a different path. Let me try a more standard Magento admin sitemap URL. In many Magento installations, the sitemap might be accessed via '/admin/admin/sitemap/' instead of being under the dashboard section.
